text: Vaccines send the immune system into perpetual overdrive by instructing cells to keep making the protein of an invader, nonstop, forever and ever.
Over-vaccination causes faster mutation of the (COVID-19) virus, which causes a super virus we may not have the ability to fight off.
Covid-19 vaccines weaken your immune system and make it harder for your body to fight the disease.
Vaccination causes the immune system to start attacking the body when the person comes into contact with coronaviruses.
Covid-19 vaccines weaken your immune system.
